    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable car that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
