      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement and fresh control arm bushings to maintain its razor-sharp handling. Mechanically robust, the Vanos system has been serviced and the valves adjusted to factory spec, ensuring peak performance across the entire 8,000 RPM powerband. It is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated engineering, offering visceral feedback and a perfectly balanced weight distribution.",
